oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Novel synthesis of trioxatetracyclo[5.3.2.0.(4,9).0(4,11)]dodecane and bibenzyl skeletons
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: REDDY, PV
MANISEKARAN, T
BHAT, SV
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: chemistry
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A novel 7,9,11-trimethyl-8,10,12-trioxatetracyclo[5.3.2.0.(4,9).0(4,11)]-dodec-1-yl]-2-butanone skeleton 3 has been synthesized by the treatment of 2-acetyl-3,4-dihydro-2,5-di (3 "-oxo-butyl)-6-methyl-(2H)-pyran 2, with H-ZSM-5. However, the treatment of compound 2 with p-TsOH gives bibenzyls. Present report provides a unique acid catalysed cyclization of diketo-olefin system over zeolite, X-ray crystal structure of 3 is also presented. (C) 1998 . .
